---
/* 2023 Scorecard – combined sections (fixed & cleaned) */
---

<!-- ================= WELCOME ================= -->
<section class="welcome">
  <div class="welcome-container">
    <h2>Welcome to the 2023 Scorecard</h2>

    <div class="welcome-grid">
      <img
        src="/images/2023/welcome.jpeg"
        alt="Solar panels with rainbow"
        class="welcome-image"
      />

      <div class="welcome-text">
        <p>
          Over the last year the solar industry has experienced unprecedented
          growth, and some significant challenges, as PV module demand and
          production have exploded across the globe. In 2023, Bloomberg New
          Energy Finance forecasts that we will surpass 300 GW of solar
          deployments globally.
        </p>

        <p>
          At this scale of project development and investment, understanding how
          to procure high-performing, reliable modules has never been more
          critical. As module buyers seek the guidance they need to navigate the
          latest technology trends and new market entrants, we are pleased to
          share with you the 9th Edition of PVEL’s PV Module Reliability
          Scorecard.
        </p>

        <a href="#">View More Message</a>

        <div class="signature">
          <strong>Luca Votta</strong>
          <span>Global Business Sector Leader</span>
          <span>Renewable Energy at Kiwa</span>
          <img src="/images/2023/kiwalogo.webp" alt="Kiwa Logo" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= BY THE NUMBERS ================= -->
<section class="numbers">
  <div class="numbers-grid">
    <!-- LEFT IMAGE -->
    <div class="numbers-image">
      <div class="numbers-overlay">
        <h2>2023 Top Performers<br />by the Numbers</h2>
        <p>Scroll through the key takeaways.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT STATS -->
    <div class="numbers-list">
      <div class="num-item">
        <span class="num">01.</span>
        <span class="label">Top Performers</span>
      </div>

      <div class="num-item">
        <span class="num">02.</span>
        <span class="label">Global Coverage</span>
      </div>

      <div class="num-item">
        <span class="num">03.</span>
        <span class="label">All Star Results</span>
      </div>

      <div class="num-item">
        <span class="num">04.</span>
        <span class="label">New Technology Increase</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= METHODOLOGY & FAILURES ================= -->
<section class="cards">
  <div class="cards-container">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Methodology</h3>

      <img src="/images/2023/methodology.jpg" alt="Testing methodology" />

      <p>
        We use a consistent methodology for testing and ranking PV modules: the
        Product Qualification Program. Our process helps buyers compare products
        across different technologies, manufacturers and model types.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our testing goes beyond the model types of PV modules to assess unique
        bill of materials (BOM) combinations.
      </p>

      <a href="#">Go to Methodology →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Failures</h3>

      <img src="/images/2023/failures.jpg" alt="Module failures" />

      <p>
        While the number of Top Performer manufacturers increased this year, so
        did the percentage of manufacturers experiencing a failure.
      </p>

      <p>
        Almost one-third of BOMs suffered at least one failure during testing,
        and 15% had a failure even before stress testing.
      </p>

      <a href="#">Go to Failures →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ---------- GLOBAL ---------- */
  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  section {
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* ---------- WELCOME ---------- */
  .welcome {
    padding: 120px 0;
  }

  .welcome-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .welcome h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .welcome-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .welcome-image {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .welcome-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .welcome-text a {
    color: #0a5bd3;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ---------- SIGNATURE ---------- */
  .signature {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .signature strong {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .signature span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .signature img {
    width: 90px;
    height: auto;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ---------- BY THE NUMBERS ---------- */
  .numbers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .numbers-image {
    aspect-ratio: 5 / 3;
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
       rgba(10, 102, 194, .551) 10%, rgba(10, 102, 194, .559) 31%, rgba(48, 65, 127, .556) 90%
      ),
      url("/images/2023/numbers.jpg") center / cover no-repeat;
    position: relative;
  }

  .numbers-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 3.5rem;
    left: 4rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .numbers-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    align-content: start;
    padding: 3rem 4rem;
    gap: 3rem;

    background: #f3f7fe;
  }

  .num-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .num {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .label {
    font-weight: 500;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* underline */
  .label::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 56px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #8f97c6;
  }

  /* ---------- CARDS ---------- */
  .cards {
    padding: 120px 0;
  }

  .cards-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card p {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .card a {
    color: #0a5bd3;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
